  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond Hanwell</h2>Step back into Hanwell and discover the world beyond it. Set in the deeper parts of London, explore Westminster and uncover the truth about yourself.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a rich, atmospheric take on Westminster and it's various Locations. Filled with lore and secrets to discover.<br></li><li>All new dual control melee combat system, land each hit and combo with satisfying intensity.<br></li><li>Scavenge scarce but available weapons and ammo with new shooting mechanics.<br></li><li>Use the environment in creative ways to take out the Anomolies. Set them on fire, electrocute them, crush them and more in frantic efforts to survive.<br></li><li>Follow the story in your own way, non linear open gameplay makes for a unique experience.<br></li><li>Immersive. All player feedback is displayed in game, with no HUD whatsoever to keep the player immersed and the tension high.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a dynamic environment. Discover locations in Westminster and uncover it's secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a6923760ca4e089eb570e7876eb9d3c0.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a6923760ca4e089eb570e7876eb9d3c0.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a6923760ca4e089eb570e7876eb9d3c0.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Beyond Hanwell is dense, detailed and atmospheric, explore, search, scavenge and survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/567a8c074a1af1c6c1fd4a105e713d8e.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/567a8c074a1af1c6c1fd4a105e713d8e.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/567a8c074a1af1c6c1fd4a105e713d8e.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore unique locations, with different creatures and boss fights in each place you visit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a08fc908f88ce900fcb88c29914611b3.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a08fc908f88ce900fcb88c29914611b3.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a08fc908f88ce900fcb88c29914611b3.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dual button combat system and punchy gunplay makes for satisfying combat encounters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/363b73ac2e1c0f5cb7efc76f1148ab86.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/363b73ac2e1c0f5cb7efc76f1148ab86.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/363b73ac2e1c0f5cb7efc76f1148ab86.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beyond Hanwell</h2>Step back into Hanwell and discover the world beyond it. Set in the deeper parts of London, explore Westminster and uncover the truth about yourself.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a rich, atmospheric take on Westminster and it's various Locations. Filled with lore and secrets to discover.<br></li><li>All new dual control melee combat system, land each hit and combo with satisfying intensity.<br></li><li>Scavenge scarce but available weapons and ammo with new shooting mechanics.<br></li><li>Use the environment in creative ways to take out the Anomolies. Set them on fire, electrocute them, crush them and more in frantic efforts to survive.<br></li><li>Follow the story in your own way, non linear open gameplay makes for a unique experience.<br></li><li>Immersive. All player feedback is displayed in game, with no HUD whatsoever to keep the player immersed and the tension high.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.webm?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/5f8f599189acbe94e7f191487f8f0ab6.mp4?t=1728122350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a dynamic environment. Discover locations in Westminster and uncover it's secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565550/extras/a6923760ca4e089eb570e7876eb9d3c0.poster.avif?t=1728122350\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s